{"tid":1728936,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環保署稱去年及今年首9月空氣中二噁英濃度沒異常","createTime":"2019-11-17T05:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T05:33:59.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ac11dd86fbb2f1433aadc03c6376a52f776400","tid":1728936,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:22:01.000Z","msg":"環保署在中西區和荃灣設監測站，監測空氣中二噁英的濃度，但上月數字至今未更新。環保署回覆本台查詢時表示，去年及今年至9月的數據顯示，二噁英日均濃度是每立方米0.009至0.086皮克，並沒發現有異常情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n警方近月大量使用催淚彈，其中內地製催淚彈不時出現大量火光，有市民關注高溫會產生二噁英。環保署表示，本港現時沒有空氣中二噁英的濃度指引，但過去3年本港錄得的二噁英濃度，遠低於加拿大安大略省的二噁英每立方米0.1皮克，和日本每立方米0.6皮克的指標。<br />\n<br />\n環保署已將上月份收集的二噁英樣本，送交政府化驗所作化學分析，一般需時數星期，預期於本月底會完成，收到報告後會盡快在網頁公布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492672-20191117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492672-20191117.htm&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz8o9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=56f4bc3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1492672-20191117.htm&h=c05c505e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1492672-20191117.htm</a>"},{"pid":"589bdb5bac18e52bdc0a1136896bb127dfaa48e8","tid":1728936,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:22:18.000Z","msg":"警：大學暴徒立即離開；五毛：立即散水；林奠建制：止暴成功，票投建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728900</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc012600cf92951e15bb6dd130773710ad67710f","tid":1728936,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa805b098e0615ca8aa18c68e500b563f26d3a3","tid":1728936,"uid":284304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"r